Lawful interception solutions are defined as the analytic tools which are used to determine the strength and direction of relationships between objects in a graph. It is a type of network analysis and increasingly being adopted for social network influencer analysis and analytics workloads. Also, the marketing managers are using this software to help in identifying their potential targets for marketing campaigns by trying to trigger chain reactions among social network communities to buy services and products. It is used for detecting financial crimes such as money laundering and is also used for detecting instances of fraud such as fraudulent transactions and types of benefits fraud in government, interceptions in banking, types of interceptions and claims fraud in insurance, and other fraudulent activities in telecommunications.

Increase in cybercrimes in the era of digitalization is a crucial factor accelerating the market growth, also increase in number of criminal activities, significant increase in interception warrants, rising surge in volume of data traffic and security threats, rise in the popularity of social media communications, rising deployment of 5G networks in all developed and developing economies, increasing number of interception warrants and rising government of both emerging and developed nations are progressively adopting lawful interception for decrypting and monitoring digital and analog information, which in turn increases the product demand and rising virtualization of advanced data centers to enhance security in virtual networks enabling vendors to offer cloud-based interception solutions are the major factors among others boosting the fixed network lawful interception market. Moreover, rising lawful interception in 5G networks, rising improvement in network technologies and rising research and development activities in the market will further create new opportunities for fixed network lawful interception market in the forecast period mentioned above.

